OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,FTwo more children's sand kits sold in
OL,7,Fthe UK have been removed from sale
OL,8,Fafter a consumer group found that they
OL,9,Fcontain asbestos.
OL,11,FThe testing by Which? follows numerous
OL,12,Fproducts ` many of them children's
OL,13,Ftoys ` being recalled from shelves
OL,14,Fbecause of asbestos contamination.
OL,16,FOne of the latest two recalls was
OL,17,Fmarketed as a Montessori sand art
OL,18,Ftray, and was being sold on Amazon
OL,19,FMarketplace and TikTok Shop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
