OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780326667
OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,FIt is designed for hands-on learning
OL,7,Fto support fine motor skills by
OL,8,Fencouraging children to draw in the
OL,9,Fsand using pencils provided in the kit
OL,10,For with their fingers.
OL,12,FWhich? testing revealed that the sand
OL,13,Fin the kit contained the banned
OL,14,Fsubstance tremolite asbestos, a
OL,15,Fharmful, naturally occurring mineral
OL,16,Fthat can become airborne and cause
OL,17,Fsevere lung diseases if inhaled, even
OL,18,Fat low levels of exposure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
