PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780326667
OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,FThe International Agency for Research
OL,7,Fon Cancer has classified all forms of
OL,8,Fasbestos as carcinogenic to humans.
OL,10,FProducts containing asbestos in any
OL,11,Fquantity, including trace amounts, are
OL,12,Fprohibited for sale in the UK.
OL,14,FA second sand art tray tested by
OL,15,FWhich? was bought from TikTok Shop and
OL,16,Fwas also found for sale from three
OL,17,Findividual sellers on Amazon
OL,18,FMarketplace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
