CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780326667
OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,FWhich? said the set remained on sale
OL,7,Fon both platforms until May, despite
OL,8,Fthe same product being subject to a
OL,9,Frecall by the Office for Product
OL,10,FSafety and Standards (OPSS) in March
OL,11,Fbecause of asbestos contamination.
OL,13,FThe OPSS has now updated the original
OL,14,Frecall notice to include Amazon and
OL,15,FTikTok Shop.
OL,17,FWhich? researchers also found
OL,18,Ftremolite asbestos in the GL Style
OL,19,FSand Bottle Art Heart or Stars set,
OL,20,Fbought from Asda and carrying the
OL,21,Fbrand name RMS International Limited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
