OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780326668
OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,FBut the watchdog also found what
OL,7,Fappeared to be the same kit for sale
OL,8,Fon eBay from three private sellers.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FMore than 39 recall notices have been
OL,16,Fissued by the OPSS since November
OL,17,Frelating to asbestos-contaminated sand
OL,18,Fproducts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
