OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780326668
OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,FThe issue has also led to the closure
OL,7,Fof schools and parks, most recently in
OL,8,FNorth East England.
OL,10,FIt is believed the affected toys
OL,11,Fcontain sand sourced from specific
OL,12,Fquarries in China, where naturally
OL,13,Foccurring asbestos is present.
OL,15,FSue Davies, head of consumer rights
OL,16,Fpolicy at Which?, said it is
OL,17,F"outrageous" that online marketplaces
OL,18,Fare selling products which may expose
OL,19,Fchildren to asbestos.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
