CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780326668
OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,F"Seemingly innocent items like toys
OL,7,Fand craft kits can have serious health
OL,8,Fconsequences if there are not proper
OL,9,Fchecks to make sure they comply with
OL,10,Fsafety laws.
OL,12,F"The longer the government delays
OL,13,Ftaking action, the greater the risk
OL,14,Fthat more dangerous products will
OL,15,Freach consumers."
OL,17,FA spokesman for Amazon said: "Customer
OL,18,Fsafety is our top priority and we are
OL,19,Ftaking this issue very seriously.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@QO]yD@^OU
