OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,F"We are in the process of removing all
OL,7,Fproducts in this category across our
OL,8,Fstore while we investigate further,
OL,9,Fand as a result the highlighted items
OL,10,Fhave been removed."
OL,12,FAsda said they began a full product
OL,13,Frecall as soon as they were made aware
OL,14,Fthat the product had failed testing.
OL,16,FThey advised customers who had bought
OL,17,Fthe product to stop using it
OL,18,Fimmediately and return it to their
OL,19,Fnearest store for a full refund.
