OL,3,CTwo more children's sand kits pulled
OL,4,Cfrom shelves over asbestos content
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for eBay said: "We
OL,7,Fswiftly removed the items identified
OL,8,Fby Which? and are conducting further
OL,9,Fsweeps to identify similar listings."
OL,11,FTikTok said the product identified
OL,12,Fduring the investigation had already
OL,13,Fbeen removed from TikTok Shop.
